data.description: Privacy at it's best! Beautiful almost 20 acres, with running creek and natural springs. Bring your horses or mini farm. This low maintenance ranch offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 large bathrooms. Inviting living room with stone fireplace and hardwood floors. Split bedroom floorplan, with 2 spacious secondary bedrooms. Expansive Master with master bathroom and walk in closets for plenty of storage. Covered rocking chair front porch. Metal Roof, vinyl siding, new well pump, new paint flooring and fixtures. This one is a must see tons of potential!
